| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 4 | 5 | 1 | 0 | 1 |
| m | n | 1 | 1 | 0 |
| 7 | 2 | 1 | 0 | 1 |

因此，答案是 `1 + 0 + 1 = 2`。
**示例 3：**
> 
`**输入：**s = "byby"`
`**输出：**0`
**解释：**
| `c` | `m` | `freq(c)` | `freq(m)` | `|freq(c) - freq(m)|` |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| b | y | 2 | 2 | 0 |

